title: Anger and Sadness After Girl Hit by Stray Bullet on Long Island Dies
text:
Published By: NYTimes NY Region - Yesterday 
The 12-year-old girl, Dejah Joyner, died at the hospital after she had been struck in the head by a bullet fired outside her home last week....
